videos.description: Kawhi Leonard explains how the Raptors were able to comeback and win Game 6, then looks ahead to their NBA Finals matchup vs. the Warriors.

videos.headline: Kawhi ready to 'take the challenge' vs. Warriors

videos.description: Giannis Antetokounmpo has high hopes for next season and says if the Bucks get better individually and as team, they will get to the next step.

videos.headline: Giannis: Bucks will be better next season

videos.description: Giannis Antetokounmpo and Khris Middleton are asked about what it means to have experience under their belts, and Giannis responds by standing up and walking out.

videos.description: Kawhi Leonard says Kyle Lowry was a pivotal force in helping him buy into the Raptors' team philosophy and make the transition from the Spurs to the Raptors.
